(\spadesuit)\:3-2(\cos(A)+\cos(B)-\cos(A)\cos(B)+\sin(A)\sin(B))\geq 0.
\begin{split}(\spadesuit)=& (\cos^2(A)+\sin^2(A)+\cos^2(B)+\sin^2(B)+1)\\-&2(\cos(A)+\cos(B)-\cos(A)\cos(B)+\sin(A)\sin(B))\\=&(\sin(A)-\sin(B))^2+(\cos(A)+\cos(B)-1)^2\geq 0.\end{split}
